            . I keep a chop-house in <placeName id="t18220220-86-crimeloc459">Coleman-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18220220-86-crimeloc459" type="placeName" value="Coleman-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18220220-86-crimeloc459" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-86-off457 t18220220-86-crimeloc459"></join>, opposite Mr. Rich's. I was standing at my door between six and seven o'clock in the evening, and saw the prisoner and a man loitering about Rich's window. I saw the prisoner go into the shop, and come out - I crossed over and took him, with a hat in his hand, and a pair of gloves in it; he said some men persuaded him to do it.</p>
